verbose_text: Despite reports that Ihh functions as a mechanotransduction mediator to promote chondrocyte proliferation during embryonic development XREF_BIBR; cell-cycle status was not altered by strain in articular chondrocytes suggesting proliferation is not increased in these cells [XREF_FIG (D)].
